Dataset¶

In [10]:
stimulus = np.array([[0,1,1],[1,1,0],[1,0,0]])
#stimulus = np.eye(3)
n_samples = 200
train = []
for _ in range(n_samples):
    r = np.random.randint(len(stimulus))
    train.append(stimulus[r])
train = np.array(train)
